  "prompt": "What are the qualities of a good mother?",
  "response": "Here are some key qualities of a good mother:\n\n1. Unconditional Love\n- Loving children consistently, regardless of their actions\n- Providing emotional support and comfort\n\n2. Patience\n- Remaining calm during challenging situations\n- Understanding child's developmental stages\n- Listening and communicating effectively\n\n3. Nurturing\n- Providing physical and emotional care\n- Ensuring child's basic needs are met\n- Promoting healthy growth and development\n\n4. Empathy\n- Understanding and validating child's feelings\n- Being supportive during difficult times\n- Showing compassion and sensitivity\n\n5. Consistent Discipline\n- Setting clear boundaries and rules\n- Teaching right from wrong\n- Using positive reinforcement\n\n6. Encouragement\n- Supporting child's goals and dreams\n- Boosting self-confidence\n- Praising effort and achievements\n\n7. Flexibility\n- Adapting parenting style as child grows\n- Being open to learning and changing\n\n8. Teaching Life Skills\n- Helping child develop independence\n- Instilling values and moral principles\n- Preparing them for future challenges\n\n9. Protection\n- Ensuring child's safety\n- Providing a secure environment\n- Advocating for child's well-being\n\n10. Self-Care\n- Maintaining personal well-being\n- Managing stress effectively\n- Being a positive role model",
